k:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 21, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104man1665703194313.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/man1665703194313.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/man1665703194313.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"man1665703194313\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get static information about clients registered with the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"man1665703194313__topic_d135047e1_d135048e1_d135049e1\">\n<p class=\"lines\" id=\"man1665703194313__lines_rfw_w5d_gwb\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation GET_CLIENTS</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code> <code class=\"ph codeph\"> string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Using</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C1)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C256)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C40)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\">: IN ; (C20)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">  entity URCLIENTS.UROUTMON : OUT</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"man1665703194313__section_gwg_2vd_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d541788e104\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"man1665703194313__ul_ab4_hvd_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Using</var>—code indicating how the clients are identified; one of: <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"man1665703194313__ul_bb4_hvd_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code> for clients with the specified host name, UST, and/or user name </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">S</code> for clients using servers with the specified host name, UST, and/or\n              user name </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var>—host name of the client or server </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var>—user name of the client or server </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var>—Uniface Server Type (UST) of the client or server </li>\n<li class=\"li\">URCLIENTS.UROUTMON—multiple occurrences of entity URCLIENTS.UROUTMON, containing client\n          information. </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">URCLIENTS.UROUTMON Entity</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">Fieldname</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">Packing Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">host</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">C256</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Host name / IP address: primary key field 1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">pid</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">I4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Process ID: primary key field 2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ust</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">C20</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Uniface server type (UST), <code class=\"ph codeph\">(MON</code>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">PRIV</code>}\n                    <code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>=Monitor, <code class=\"ph codeph\">(MY MON</code>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">PRIV</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>=this\n                    Monitor,<code class=\"ph codeph\">PRIV</code>=privileged Monitor, <code class=\"ph codeph\">(WEB Client)</code>=WRD</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">user</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">C40</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">O/S user name</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">connet</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">C3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Connection network to Uniface Router (e.g. <code class=\"ph codeph\">TCP</code>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">conaddr</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">C8</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Connection address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port number)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">server</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">C80</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Server or hop, for example:<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ora:|u|p /ex\n                    /su</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">tcp:h|u|p|myust</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">constamp</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__2\">E5</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__3\">Datetime</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"man1665703194313__table_w5413ab1b5b3b5_w5414ab1b5b3_w5415ab1b5_w5416ab1__entry__4\">Client connected at dd-mmm-yyyy hh:mm:ss</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The order of clients is undefined. The selection criteria <var class=\"keyword varname\">Host</var>,\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var> and/or <var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var>, if present, are combined (logical\n        AND) and applied to running servers or clients to select the list of clients.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"man1665703194313__section_t13_cxd_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d541788e380\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If successful, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to the number (&gt;=0) of returned\n                URCLIENTS occurrences. Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"man1665703194313__section_zlg_2xd_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d541788e396\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"man1665703194313__section_i5w_2xd_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d541788e405\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">GET_CLIENTS</span> operation gets static information about clients\n        registered with the Uniface Router.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529812\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529812\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "GET_CLIENTS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 21, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get static information about clients registered with the Uniface Router. operation GET_CLIENTS params string Using : IN ; (C1) string Host : IN ; (C256) string User : IN ; (C40) string UST : IN ; (C20) entity URCLIENTS.UROUTMON : OUT endparams Parameters Using —code indicating how the clients are identified; one of: C for clients with the specified host name, UST, and/or user name S for clients using servers with the specified host name, UST, and/or user name Host —host name of the client or server User —user name of the client or server UST —Uniface Server Type (UST) of the client or server URCLIENTS.UROUTMON—multiple occurrences of entity URCLIENTS.UROUTMON, containing client information. Table 1. URCLIENTS.UROUTMON Entity Fieldname Packing Code Data Type Description host C256 String Host name / IP address: primary key field 1 pid I4 Numeric Process ID: primary key field 2 ust C20 String Uniface server type (UST), (MON { PRIV } ) =Monitor, (MY MON { PRIV } ) =this Monitor, PRIV =privileged Monitor, (WEB Client) =WRD user C40 String O/S user name connet C3 String Connection network to Uniface Router (e.g. TCP ) conaddr C8 String Connection address on Uniface Router (e.g. the port number) server C80 String Server or hop, for example: ora:|u|p /ex /su or tcp:h|u|p|myust constamp E5 Datetime Client connected at dd-mmm-yyyy hh:mm:ss The order of clients is undefined. The selection criteria Host , User and/or UST , if present, are combined (logical AND) and applied to running servers or clients to select the list of clients. Return Values If successful, $status is set to the number (>=0) of returned URCLIENTS occurrences. Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The GET_CLIENTS operation gets static information about clients registered with the Uniface Router. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}